round2 = function(x, n = 0) {
  
  posneg = sign(x)
  z = abs(x)*10^n
  z = z + 0.5 + sqrt(.Machine$double.eps)
  z = trunc(z)
  z = z/10^n
  z*posneg
  
} #      

round(0.5) ; round2(0.5, 0) #    n digits

# 3. data load

for (k in seq_along(CORE)) { # k = 1, 2    
  
  temp1 <- tibble() #    
  
  for (i in seq_along(NUMBER)) { # i = 1, 2, ... , 86    
    
    URL <- paste0(BASE, # URL  
                  '101/', # 
                  'DT_1KS2015/', #  (2015=100)
                  '2/', # 
                  '1/', #  : 1
                  CORE[k], '_', NUMBER[i], # URL 
                  '&prdSe=', 'M', #  : Month
                  '&newEstPrdCnt=', '1') #  1 
    
    temp2 <- tryCatch(expr = fromJSON(URL) %>% # fromJSON ~ select  ,
                             tibble() %>% 
                             mutate( = i) %>% 
                             select(, PRD_DE, ITM_NM, C1_NM, C1, DT),
                      error = function(e) tibble(NULL)) # ( )  
    
    temp1 <- rbind(temp2, temp1) # stacking
    
  }
  
  temp3 <- temp1 %>% 
    arrange(nchar(C1), C1) %>% #     
    mutate_at(vars(DT), as.double) #  class  
  
  DATA <- rbind(temp3, DATA) # stacking
  
}

# 3. crawling

PERIOD <- 2000:2021 # 2000~2021   vector 

MASTERPIECE <- tibble() #    

for (i in seq_along(PERIOD)) { # i = 1, 2, ..., 22    
  
  URL <- paste0('https://www.melon.com/chart/age/index.htm',
                '?chartType=YE',
                '&chartGenre=KPOP',
                '&chartDate=', PERIOD[i]) #     
  
  REMDR$navigate(URL) # URL 
  
  temp1 <- REMDR$getPageSource() #   
  
  TITLE <- read_html(temp1[[1]]) %>% # html    
    html_elements('form#frm') %>% # form#frm 
    html_elements('div.wrap_song_info') %>% # div.wrap_song_info 
    html_elements('div.ellipsis.rank01') %>% # div.ellipsis.rank01 
    html_text() %>% #  
    str_remove_all('\n') %>% #  '\n' 
    str_remove_all('\t') %>% #  '\t'  
    str_sub(end = -2) #     
  
  SINGER <- read_html(temp1[[1]]) %>%
    html_elements('form#frm') %>%
    html_elements('div.wrap_song_info') %>%
    html_elements('div.ellipsis.rank02') %>%
    html_text() %>%
    str_sub(end = nchar(.)/2) #       
  
  ALBUM <- read_html(temp1[[1]]) %>%
    html_elements('form#frm') %>%
    html_elements('div.wrap_song_info') %>%
    html_elements('div.ellipsis.rank03') %>%
    html_text() %>%
    str_remove_all('\n') %>%
    str_remove_all('\t')
  
  LIKE <- read_html(temp1[[1]]) %>%
    html_elements('button.btn_icon.like') %>%
    html_text() %>%
    str_remove_all('\n\n\n') %>% #  
    str_remove_all(',') %>% #  
    as.integer() #      integer class 
  
  temp2 <- tibble(YEAR = PERIOD[i], RANK = 1:100, 
                  TITLE, SINGER, ALBUM, LIKE) #    temp2 
  
  MASTERPIECE <- rbind(MASTERPIECE, temp2) #   
  
  Sys.sleep(5 + rnorm(1)) #  ,    5 
  
}
